      "description": "THE TAX DEADLINE IS 4/15. FILE WITH AN EXPERT AS SOON AS TODAY.\n• Grab your docs, and let TurboTax take it from here.\n• Connect with one of our thousands of tax experts on-demand. Expert help is just a click away (4).\n\nHAND OFF YOUR TAXES TO A LOCAL EXPERT WHO HAS YOUR BACK\n• Get matched with an expert based on your unique tax situation.\n• Your expert prepares your return from start to finish, and you'll get real time updates on their progress.* (*Available in iOS only)\n• Your expert will only sign and file when they know your return is 100% correct and you’re getting the best outcome possible (1).\n\nOTHER WAYS TO FILE\nFREE FILING OPTION FOR SIMPLE TAX RETURNS \nTurboTax Free Edition: $0 federal returns + $0 state returns = $0 to file. ~37% of taxpayers qualify. Simple Form 1040 returns only (no schedules except for Earned Income Tax Credit, Child Tax Credit, and Student Loan Interest, and Schedule 1-A). (2)\n\nWHEN YOU FINISH FILING, GET MONEY FAST\n• Up to 5 Days Early Refund: Get your federal tax refund up to 5 days before IRS delivery in your own bank account for a fee (3). Terms apply.\n\nFILE EASILY WITH SPECIAL APP FEATURES\n• File your tax return 30% faster on our app!*\n• Get started quickly with easy info uploads. Snap a photo, upload your docs, or import your tax forms directly from your employer or financial institution, and we’ll auto-fill your info.\n• Spanish-language support: You can now toggle between English and Spanish and file your taxes in your preferred language. Bilingual experts are also available to help you file your taxes or do them for you.\n\nREADY TO FILE WITH CONFIDENCE? Download the TurboTax app today and get your maximum refund, guaranteed.\n\nDISCLAIMERS\n1. Guarantees: See terms of service or turbotax.com/guarantees for full details.\n2. TurboTax Free Edition: TurboTax Free Edition is available for those filing simple Form 1040 returns and limited credits only (no forms or schedules except for the Earned Income Tax Credit, Child Tax Credit, and student loan interest, and Schedule 1-A), as detailed in the TurboTax Free Edition disclosures. Roughly 37% of taxpayers qualify. Offer may change or end at any time without notice.\n3. Up to 5 Days Early Refund: Money movement services by Intuit Payments Inc., licensed by NYDFS.\n4. Unlimited access to TurboTax experts is included with all Expert Assist and Expert Full Service products.\n5. Intuit is an independent company with no affiliation to any government entity. This TurboTax app also doesn't represent any government entity. The websites for the IRS: https://www.irs.gov, as well as state & local tax authorities listed here: https://ttlc.intuit.com/turbotax-support/en-us/help-article/state-taxes/contact-state-department-revenue/L9qVToi02_US_en_US are the source of information for specific tax requirements.\nIntuit has offices worldwide, and is headquartered in Mountain View, 2700 Coast Ave, Mountain View, CA 94043.",
